    com.atakmap.android.fires.bridge.RemarksConstants
    these constants have been moved to gov.tak.api.fires.LineBase. When removed, existing meta value keys will no longer exist at the root level of 5 and 9-line target MapItems. "nineLine" and "fiveLine" keys pointing to AttributeSet representations of the new LineBase models will replace them. These AttributeSets can be marshalled to LineBase, gov.tak.api.fires.FiveLine or gov.tak.api.fires.NineLine.
